## Version

`tailwind@4.0.0-beta.2` and `@tailwindcss/vite@4.0.0-beta.2`

## Environment

Output of `npx envinfo --system --binaries --browsers --npmPackages "{vite,tailwindcss,@tailwindcss/*,postcss-mixins}"`:

```
